{"id":145247,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/04/【组图】这只是几十年前的中国/","date":"2011-04-18T04:00:36Z","modified":"2011-04-18T04:00:36Z","title":"【组图】这只是几十年前的中国","content":"<p><img src=\"http://dongxi.net/upload/attached/2011/04/20110408100428_10398.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://dongxi.net/upload/attached/2011/04/20110408100419_59735.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://dongxi.net/upload/attached/2011/04/20110408100430_49273.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br />\n过去两个世纪是科技和文明的飞速发展的两个世纪。科技和文明的发展彻底改变了人类的生活方式。如果你看到人们几十年前是如何生活的，而今又是如何，你会发现技术的发展速度有多么惊人。当然，不是全世界的发展速度都相同，但在过去30年几乎世界的每一个角落一生活方式都在迅速改变。<br />\n中国很长一段时间在贫困线上挣扎，但最终，经济发展有了成效，带来了改变。这里的照片，仅仅是几十年前的中国。<br />\n<img src=\"http://dongxi.net/upload/attached/2011/04/20110408100430_75092.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://dongxi.net/upload/attached/2011/04/20110408100418_55048.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://dongxi.net/upload/attached/2011/04/20110408100403_18201.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://dongxi.net/upload/attached/2011/04/20110408100449_34896.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://dongxi.net/upload/attached/2011/04/20110408100434_39294.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://dongxi.net/upload/attached/2011/04/20110408100415_61928.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://dongxi.net/upload/attached/2011/04/20110408100432_74962.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://dongxi.net/upload/attached/2011/04/20110408100457_69828.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://dongxi.net/upload/attached/2011/04/20110408110424_13167.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://dongxi.net/upload/attached/2011/04/20110408110456_43263.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://dongxi.net/upload/attached/2011/04/20110408110422_54092.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedb